<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><lyrics>[V1]
 wǒ men gǎn xiè tiān fù de ài, ràng wǒ jīn tiān jiàn dào nǐ.
 wǒ men zhàn zài yé hé huá de mén nèi, xīn zhōng hé děng kuài lè huān xǐ.
 shén de ér nǚ xìng qǐ xìng qǐ, qǐ lái zàn měi zào nǐ de zhǔ.
 yīn wèi quán de dōu yào zàn měi tā, quán de dōu yào xiàng tā huān hū.
 hā lì lù yà tiān fù de ài wú rén néng chàng wán wú rén néng cè dù.
 wǒ men xiāng jù xiāng jù zài cǎi hóng xià, xiàng tiān fù xiàn shàng zàn měi.</lyrics>
<title>tiān fù de ài 迦南736</title>
<author>lǚ xiǎo mǐn</author>
<hymn_number>736</hymn_number>
</song>